Item 8.01. Other Events.
On July 8, 2025, United States District Court for the Northern District of California (the “Court”) preliminarily approved the settlement (“Settlement”) of a stockholder derivative action captioned In re Alphabet Inc. Shareholder Derivative Litigation, Consolidated Case No. 3:21-cv-09388-RFL (the “Action”). Pursuant to the Court’s order granting preliminary approval of the Settlement, Alphabet Inc. (the “Company”) is required to publish the Notice of Pendency and Proposed Settlement of Derivative Action (the “Notice”), attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1. The Notice and the Stipulation and Agreement of Settlement (“Stipulation”) are available for review on the Company’s Investor Relations website at https://abc.xyz/investor/. As noted in the Stipulation, the defendants deny any liability in connection with the claims alleged in the Action.
